io.github.jonestimd.swing.layout

Class GridBagBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.jonestimd.swing.layout.GridBagBuilder

  • public class GridBagBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
    A form builder that simplifies usage of GridBagLayout. The initial constraints are as follows
    • (gridx, gridy) = (0, 0)
    • fill = HORIZONTAL
    • weightx, weighty = 1.0
    • anchor = WEST
    The constraints are updated using a GridBagFormula when each component is added.

    The following components are automatically wrapped in a JScrollPane:

    • JTable
    • JList
    • JTextArea
